I just made a little patch for people who use the interstage decoupler mostly as a top node decoupler and retrorocket, to just switch the default decoupling nodes and rocket orientation:

@PART[SSTU-SC-GEN-ISDC]:NEEDS[SSTU]:AFTER[SSTU]  

{  

    @MODULE[ModuleDecouple]  

    {  

        @stagingEnabled = true  

    }  

    @MODULE[SSTUInterstageDecoupler]  

    {  

        @stagingEnabled = false  

        %invertEngines = true  

    }  

}
